@deborahkass (along with artist Chuck Close) was commissioned to do the Democratic National Convention poster in 2016, Here is comparison of Deb's with Warhol's DNC poster for McGovern in 1972, google.com/search?q=deb+kass…

This afternoon at the High Ridge Country Club in Palm Beach, Fla. I am pleased to have Lisa Dennison, Sotheby's Chairman of the Americas and my sister @deborahkass as participants in our Culture Sundays project. Like Sly Stone sang, this is a family affair!

Lisa, was formerly Director of The Guggenheim Museum before she joined Sothebys - she is my son's godmother. Deb's work is in many of the major art museums in the U.S. piped.video/watch?v=i3mYv3WH… and her Oy/Yo sculpture has just been placed in front of The Brooklyn Musuem.
